  "name": "Error when using Tyro payment option in Retail Express Hardware Utility",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"error-when-using-tyro-payment-option-in-retail-express-hardware-utility\">Error when using Tyro payment option in Retail Express Hardware Utility</h1>\n<p><span>If receive an error when using Tyro payment option.</span></p>\n<p><span>There are 2 Possible errors with the Tyro payment option.</span></p>\n<ol><li><strong>Tyro adapter is installed and a REX utility error occurred - REF Picture 1</strong>\n<ol><li>When opening the Tyro Adapter and upon closing an error occurs in Retail Express Hardware Utility (crashing the service).</li></ol></li><li><strong>Unsupported 16-bit Application Error - REF Picture 2</strong></li></ol><p><span>Ref pictures below:</span></p>\na. <img alt=\"rtaImage (86).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox20EAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><br/>b. <img alt=\"rtaImage (87).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox25EAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/> <br/><hr></hr><p> </p>\n<h2 data-id=\"tyro-adapter-is-installed-and-a-rex-utility-error-occurred-ref-picture-1\">Tyro adapter is installed and a REX utility error occurred - REF Picture 1</h2>\n<p>Ensure you are logged in as Admin</p>\n<ol><li>Download the Registry edit file below, open and run the file in the PC with the error.</li><li>Rerun the Retail Express Hardware Utility and the Tyro adapter should no longer crash the service.</li></ol><p> </p>\n<hr></hr><h2 data-id=\"unsupported-16-bit-application-error-ref-picture-2\">Unsupported 16-bit Application Error - REF Picture 2</h2>\n<ol><li>Press <strong>OK</strong> on the error message</li><li>Press <strong>Back</strong> in the REX utility</li><li>Download the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.tyro.com%2Fs%2Farticle%2FHow-do-I-install-the-Tyro-Terminal-Adapter\">Tyro Adapter</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.tyro.com%2Fs%2F\">Tyro's Knowledge Base</a>\n<ol><li>You may Google <strong>Tyro Adapter</strong></li><li>Or use this link <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.tyro.com%2Fs%2Farticle%2FHow-do-I-install-the-Tyro-Terminal-Adapter\">https://help.tyro.com/s/article/How-do-I-install-the-Tyro-Terminal-Adapter</a></li></ol></li><li>Download the adapter and install<br/><img alt=\"rtaImage (88).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pox2AEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Press Next in REX utility and the configuration button should be enabled.</li></ol>",
